{"tid":274002,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"世 界 級 滅 火 教 材 ！ ！ ！","createTime":"2017-06-07T03:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T07:53:34.000Z","uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"644d47038238e7cf3ac0459817c673ac88a28b41","tid":274002,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:59:06.000Z","msg":"學妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 學長，為什麼剛進去的時候，你都會射上面？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 因為射上面 比較安全啊！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 那進去的時候呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :進去的時候，還是會射。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 那不會有危險嗎...?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 其實只要進去，都很危險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進入火場時，務必先以水柱掃射天花板，將可能的掉落物掃除，深入火場時， 水線切勿中斷，注意周圍安全，處處充滿危險。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0341e51ad344076eb38405a3e331021dd51b0f61","tid":274002,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/ce/WOW%21.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20061012041900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fce%2FWOW%2521.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20061012041900&h=0744ff9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02ff06a81a702108dfcbfca783dbaf88656a677f","tid":274002,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T04:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://vignette3.